{"about_the_game":"Take flight in this casual adventure game as a bee on a mission to save your crumbling hive. With the Queen mysteriously missing, it's up to you to gather resources like pollen and nectar to rebuild your home, explore the vast Aurora Basin, and embark on quests across the land to help the animals of nature as you become the hero your hive needs!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038640/extras/CollectGif.gif?t=1736886113\" /><br><br>With the Queen missing, the hive is struggling to survive. There are few bees left to forage for the hive. Fly out into the vibrant world to collect all the staples a bee needs: pollen, nectar, and propolis. You may even find a few rare flowers along the way! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038640/extras/CustomizeGif.gif?t=1736886113\" /><br><br>Help get the bees back on their wings! The hive is in desperate need of repair and you know just what they need. Reopen shops to customize your bee with vibrant colors or fun hats, rebuild rooms to attract more bees back to the basin, and even fix up a dance floor to show off your moves! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038640/extras/AnimalGif.gif?t=1736886113\" /><br><br>Bees hold ecosystems together! Animals across the entire basin rely on your assistance. From helping a lost fawn find its way home to resolving disputes between wildlife, you can help restore the balance of nature and make new friends along the way!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3038640/extras/ExploreGif.gif?t=1736886113\" /><br><br>Explore the vast and diverse Aurora Basin! From the snowy mountain peaks to the scorching heat of the desert, there are unique areas to visit with secrets to be found.","background":"https://shared.akama